<plot>1920's, The Ditch, lead singer of Tab on Sank, has an itch to be in the mafia, hey everyone does don't they? He kills Fifi Fandango, famous poisoner, and mafia crony. He then gets stalked by Don Taliana's men, thinking they are out to kill him he hides around town. 'The Gentleman' and Tommy 'The Sax', dastardly capos of the Don's track him down, he flees with them hot on his tail. Once captured he meets the Don of Don's himself, Don Taliana. Who indoctrinates our Anti Hero into the mafiosi. Everybodies happy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?042977</url></doc>
